<html lang='vi'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Xác nhận Email</title>
    <link
      href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap'
      rel='stylesheet'
    />
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        background-color: #eef4fb;
        font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
        padding: 40px 16px;
      }

      .wrapper {
        max-width: 520px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d7dd2 0%, #3a9bd5 100%);
        border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
        padding: 28px 32px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo-wrap {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .logo-icon {
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .logo-text {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        letter-spacing: -0.3px;
      }

      .logo-text span {
        color: #bde0ff;
      }

      .card {
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 40px 36px 32px;
        border-left: 1px solid #dbeafe;
        border-right: 1px solid #dbeafe;
      }

      .icon-circle {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff8ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border: 2px solid #bfdbfe;
      }

      .icon-circle svg {
        width: 28px;
        height: 28px;
        stroke: #2d7dd2;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #0f1f3d;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        letter-spacing: -0.4px;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #64748b;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      .subtitle strong {
        color: #2d7dd2;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .divider {
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(
          to right,
          transparent,
          #dbeafe,
          transparent
        );
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .btn-wrap {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 13px 36px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d7dd2 0%, #3a9bd5 100%);
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.2px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(45, 125, 210, 0.35);
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }

      .expiry {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 6px;
        background: #eff8ff;
        border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 10px 16px;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .expiry svg {
        width: 15px;
        height: 15px;
        stroke: #2d7dd2;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .expiry span {
        font-size: 12.5px;
        color: #2d7dd2;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .fallback {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .fallback p {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #94a3b8;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .fallback a {
        font-size: 11.5px;
        color: #3a9bd5;
        word-break: break-all;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer {
        background: #f0f7ff;
        border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
        border-top: none;
        border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
        padding: 20px 32px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .footer p {
        font-size: 11.5px;
        color: #94a3b8;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #2d7dd2;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='wrapper'>

      <div class='header'>
        <div class='logo-wrap'>
          <div class='logo-icon'>
            <svg
              width='18'
              height='18'
              viewBox='0 0 24 24'
              fill='none'
              stroke='white'
              stroke-width='2.5'
              stroke-linecap='round'
              stroke-linejoin='round'
            >
              <circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10' />
              <path d='M8 12l3 3 5-5' />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class='logo-text'>Moto<span>Market</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='card'>

        <div class='icon-circle'>
          <svg
            viewBox='0 0 24 24'
            fill='none'
            stroke-width='2'
            stroke-linecap='round'
            stroke-linejoin='round'
          >
            <path d='M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8' />
            <rect x='2' y='6' width='20' height='13' rx='2' />
          </svg>
        </div>

        <h1>Xác nhận địa chỉ email</h1>
        <p class='subtitle'>
          Xin chào
          <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>! Cảm ơn bạn đã đăng ký.<br />
          Vui lòng nhấn nút bên dưới để kích hoạt tài khoản của bạn.
        </p>

        <div class='divider'></div>

        <div class='btn-wrap'>
          <a href='{{verificationLink}}' class='button'>
            ✉️ &nbsp; Xác nhận Email
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class='expiry'>
          <svg
            viewBox='0 0 24 24'
            fill='none'
            stroke-width='2'
            stroke-linecap='round'
            stroke-linejoin='round'
          >
            <circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10' />
            <polyline points='12 6 12 12 16 14' />
          </svg>
          <span>Liên kết sẽ hết hạn sau <strong>15 phút</strong></span>
        </div>

        <div class='fallback'>
          <p>Nếu nút không hoạt động, sao chép liên kết sau vào trình duyệt:</p>
          <a href='{{verificationLink}}'>{{verificationLink}}</a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>
          Nếu bạn không thực hiện yêu cầu này, vui lòng bỏ qua email này.<br />
          Tài khoản sẽ không được kích hoạt nếu không xác nhận.<br />
          <a href='#'>Hủy đăng ký</a>
          &nbsp;·&nbsp;
          <a href='#'>Trợ giúp</a>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>